s, all of whom are seeking to showcase investment opportunities in their countries and communities.    The presidential candidate of the Social Democratic Party, SDP, Prince Adewole Adebayo, has said he would have the full weight of the law on incessant attacks in the country even as he reaffirmed  his party's commitment to religious freedom in the country. Adebayo made the remarks as a guest of the… In "News" From left: Prince Adewole Adebayo, SDP presidential candidate; a guest and Dr. Ralph Bello-Fadile at the event. The Social Democratic Party, SDP’s presidential candidate, Prince Adewole Adebayo, has said that a stable Nigeria can take off many burdens which the United States bears in Africa. He described US Deputy Secretary… In "Politics" Prince Adewole Adebayo(4th left); Prof Pat Utomi(4th right) and other dignitaries at the event. The Social Democratic Party, SDP, candidate in the 2023 Nigerian presidential election, Prince Adewole Adebayo, has said for Nigeria to be free of the malice stunting her growth and preventing her attaining full potential, the people,… In "News"